{"TopicId":225381,"ForumId":119,"TopicTitle":"A week since the purge","CreatedByName":"RUD Everyday","CreatedById":228396,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-09T01:53:59Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"RUD Everyday","CreatedById":228396,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-09T01:53:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have come to call the death of KSP2 \u0022The Purge\u0022and it has been a week since, thoughts?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scarecrow71","CreatedById":210112,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-09T01:55:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224405821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022225381\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221720490039\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022228396\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RUD Everyday\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Rapid unplanned disassembly\u0022\u003ERUD\u003C/abbr\u003E Everyday said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthoughts?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think we should use one of the million other threads that are out there for specifically talking about this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-09T03:07:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree, Comment in before thread locked. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESeriously though we have enough 502s without adding threads to do what other threads are already set up for.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Izny","CreatedById":137814,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-09T10:13:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224405839\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022225381\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221720494476\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211123\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ColdJ\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, ColdJ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree, Comment in before thread locked. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESeriously though we have enough 502s without adding threads to do what other threads are already set up for.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe 502 and 503 errors have got nothing to do with that though ^^\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rebel-1","CreatedById":170896,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-09T11:21:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis crying is getting too much.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-09T12:24:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224405927\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022225381\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221720519984\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022137814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Izny\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Izny said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe 502 and 503 errors have got nothing to do with that though ^^\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen the 502s are bad, each thread you have to open up to see a new comment, is a thread that might not open. So if all the same type of comments are all in the same thread then when you finally get it to load, you can read that page without having then to open yet another. It is the little things in life. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Izny","CreatedById":137814,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-09T12:29:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224405982\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022225381\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221720527853\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211123\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ColdJ\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, ColdJ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen the 502s are bad, each thread you have to open up to see a new comment, is a thread that might not open. So if all the same type of comments are all in the same thread then when you finally get it to load, you can read that page without having then to open yet another. It is the little things in life. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthere\u0027s not enough traffic volume on ksp forums for a company like take two to have any excuses of them running into capacity issues though \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FiendChain","CreatedById":228883,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-09T15:06:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeople might be trying to scrape all of the pages in the forum for a possible imminent forum closure. Started really getting 502/503 errors once Vanamode hinted that the forums might be closed down in the future and it got shared to reddit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-09T15:50:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf multiple threads on a topic exist, please do not start another one. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}